    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BackStreet 是一款融合了快节奏、风格化连击动作与战略成长的 3D 动作类 Roguelite 游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/939d6426e34d8a038a2477dca27afbcd.poster.avif?t=1770599106\" width=800 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/939d6426e34d8a038a2477dca27afbcd.webm?t=1770599106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/e3481cbf1f9e8c1a45558d5d4c6d4f87.poster.avif?t=1770599106\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/e3481cbf1f9e8c1a45558d5d4c6d4f87.webm?t=1770599106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/e3481cbf1f9e8c1a45558d5d4c6d4f87.mp4?t=1770599106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在因环境污染而荒废的城市中生存，普通攻击连击、冲刺攻击连击、跳跃攻击连击，适应敌人的攻击模式，展开动态战斗。与堕落的 3COS 机械战斗，获取新技能，打造属于自己的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/4ab85a7ba854785e9a39980878469bcd.poster.avif?t=1770599106\" width=800 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/4ab85a7ba854785e9a39980878469bcd.webm?t=1770599106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/60df6d041a69630b1a60c3efefe6f22f.poster.avif?t=1770599106\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/60df6d041a69630b1a60c3efefe6f22f.webm?t=1770599106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/60df6d041a69630b1a60c3efefe6f22f.mp4?t=1770599106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败所有敌人后提供的<strong>增幅芯片</strong>是自定义战斗风格的关键手段。通过分析从机器人残骸中获取的数据，你可以对敌人施加各种致命的减益效果。寻找最佳的连招与减益组合，增强自身能力，并继续找回失去的身份的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/08faae47395f0cb634f42e911c64229a.poster.avif?t=1770599106\" width=800 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/08faae47395f0cb634f42e911c64229a.webm?t=1770599106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/2ff31943f1619fc94b6878ef33f1b70e.poster.avif?t=1770599106\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/2ff31943f1619fc94b6878ef33f1b70e.webm?t=1770599106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121410/extras/2ff31943f1619fc94b6878ef33f1b70e.mp4?t=1770599106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地球已变得不适合人类生存，只有被派遣来恢复生态的机器人仍然留在这里。击败掌控城市的人工智能 3COS，揭开人类与自己的真实故事。</p>",
